title: Darlin’ You Trend Me 2/14: Heart Shaped Pizza, Stranger Things, Banksy, Fantasy Island

description:
On this Valentine’s Day edition of Darlin’ You Trend Me Jack and Miles discuss heart shaped pizzas, the first Stranger Things (4) trailer, Banksy has a new piece in Bristol, and a fresh trailer for Fantasy Island.
